---
description: General Broadcast Graphics project rules
alwaysApply: true
---

This repository is an MVP for broadcast graphics. Preserve working behavior over theoretical production hardening.

Follow these rules:

- Respond and document project-facing guidance in Russian unless source code naming requires English.
- Read relevant files before editing.
- Keep changes scoped to the requested product zone.
- If you need to edit outside the current owner zone, explain why and ask before proceeding.
- Do not add auth, complex DB, deployment platform, or large dependency upgrades unless explicitly requested.
- Do not edit plan files unless explicitly requested.
- Do not commit or push unless explicitly requested.
- Preserve the manual baseline in `docs/baseline-checklist.md`.

Current product zones:

- Sergey: `frontend/src/features/editor/**`, editor UI and editor interactions.
- Vasily: templates, rundowns, external integrations, control UI around templates/rundowns.
- Team lead: backend core, shared contracts, LLM, repo process, architecture.

Before PR:

- `npm run typecheck`
- `npm run build`
- manual startup via `./start.sh`
